Users without primary extension:
select enduser.userid,numplan.dnorpattern as extension, routepartition.name as partition
from enduser
left join enduserdevicemap as edmap on enduser.pkid = edmap.fkenduser
left join device on device.pkid = edmap.fkdevice
left join devicenumplanmap as dnmap on device.pkid = dnmap.fkdevice
left join numplan on numplan.pkid = dnmap.fknumplan
left join routepartition on numplan.fkroutepartition = routepartition.pkid
where userid not in (
	select userid
	from endusernumplanmap as map
	left join enduser as e on e.pkid = map.fkenduser
	left join numplan on numplan.pkid = map.fknumplan
	where tkdnusage =1)
